September 2025
<p>New NSF grant received ($0.9M).</p>

April 2025
<p>Bosheng Li and Xiaochen Zhou successfully defended their Ph.D. theses!</p>

April 2025
<p>Our new neural ranking algorithm <a href='https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/10950450'> TreeStructor </a> allows for a full forest reconstruction from point clouds.</p>

January 2025
<p>Another news about out Tree D-Fusion project. at <a href='https://ag.purdue.edu/news/2025/03/3d-tree-reconstruction-algorithm-contributes-to-a-new-era-of-urban-planning.html'> Purdue News, </a> <a href='https://www.eurekalert.org/news-releases/1075541'> Eureka Alert </a>, and <a href='https://techxplore.com/news/2025-03-3d-tree-reconstruction-algorithm-contributes.html'> TechXplore </a></p>

January 2025
<p>Some news about out Tree D-Fusion project. at <a href='https://www.planetizen.com/news/2025/01/133724-how-ai-revolutionizing-urban-forestry-and-climate-resilience'> Planetizen, </a> <a href='https://woodcentral.com.au/hey-google-data-scientists-use-ai-to-plant-new-forests-in-the-cities/'> Woodcentral </a>, and <a href='https://www.thecooldown.com/green-tech/tree-d-fusion-ai-tool-cities-urban-landscapes/'> the Cooldown </a></p>

